'''Runyip stew''' was a dish that contained [[Runyip/Legends|runyip]] meat which [[Kyle Katarn]] had during his trip aboard ''[[Star of Empire]]''. Runyip stew was also on the menu of [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker's]] [[Jedi Praxeum]] on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]]. [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] ate a bowl there along with a side of mixed [[Color/Legends|green]] vegetables.

